{"title":"翻身农奴心中的歌","authors":["温民法　周鹤"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身农奴心中的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温民法　周鹤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍红檀香木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用金子的斧头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍白檀香木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用银子的斧头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耘拉萨河谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能用缓慢的牦牛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席派来了拖拉机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在无垠的田野里奔走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镂珊瑚花的金杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用来盛芬芳的青稞酒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雕格桑花的银瓶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用来盛喷香的酥油。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金箭一样的青稞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能用双手去拔收？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席派来了收割机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把金色的海洋搬走！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}